Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:05.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:13.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.69,0:00:33.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.44,0:00:36.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sound resonates\NInto my heart, so hard and deep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.31,0:00:40.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A field of stars spans endlessly\NAnd through it I carve a passageway
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.31,0:00:42.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In step with time as generations change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.31,0:00:44.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes and listen closely
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.31,0:00:47.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting stars stream on silently…\Nuntil the goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.31,0:00:50.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the light inside of you,\Nnever give up don't ever lose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.31,0:00:52.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Transcend time and you will prove,\Nthere is a special place for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.27,0:00:54.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A blaze of glory is there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:55.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a part of our estate;\Nlife is our story to create
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.86,0:01:01.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.77,0:01:05.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old by voice of light\NThroughout the age, never fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.69,0:01:09.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A secret fire, a scream of light,\Nvoices calling through twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:11.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cast your thoughts to the wind,\Nhang your wishes on the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:13.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Live your life with all your strength\Nfor dreams will reach you very soon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.48,0:01:16.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.07,0:01:19.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old\Nby voice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.27,0:01:21.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Throughout the age,\Nnever fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:24.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someday your dream will find\Nits place somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.82,0:01:28.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep shining like a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:42.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.96,0:01:48.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain of the Squad 3,\NGin Ichimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.27,0:01:52.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.62,0:02:10.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jidanbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.17,0:02:22.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:28.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A guardian of the gate isn't supposed\Nto open the gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.94,0:02:33.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We were careless…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.93,0:02:37.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect that someone like him\Nwould come all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:41.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if these kids have\Nbecome strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:44.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain level’s strength is\Nbeyond imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:47.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They cannot fight him…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.69,0:02:50.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We must avoid that\Nworst possible scenario!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.16,0:02:56.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh… I lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:03:01.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Opening the gate is what is expected\Nof a gatekeeper who has lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:05.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:09.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A gatekeeper who lost isn't\Nopening any gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:12.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When a gatekeeper loses…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:15.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,it means…"death."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:24.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:31.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:34.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:39.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come now and try to butt in,\Nyou fox face!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.37,0:03:43.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who'd attack\Nan unarmed guy…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:45.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,will be killed by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.29,0:03:48.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! You're a funny kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:51.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're not scared of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:52.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:53.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.37,0:03:57.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it Ichigo!\NWe will retreat for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:03:59.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:02.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:01.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So then…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:03.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only just getting started!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:04.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:05.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way I can forgive guys like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:06.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:08.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just end it…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:10.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Ichigo Kurosaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:14.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You know about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:18.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:24.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Hey! Where're you going?!\NHey wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.12,0:04:29.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All the more reason why\NI can't let you pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:37.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you standing so far back?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:40.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to throw\Nyour short sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:45.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a short sword.\NThis is my Zanpaku-to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:56.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Impale him, Shinso!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:12.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:13.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:16.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:17.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The gate…!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:21.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:30.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Owwee!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.58,0:05:29.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Kurosaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:30.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:34.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The gate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:37.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:41.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.58,0:05:45.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry…the gate closed because of me…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:51.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, your opponent was Gin Ichimaru.\NIt couldn't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:54.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Be glad that you weren't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:04.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:04.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:06.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:07.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:15.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:17.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They were hiding until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:19.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:22.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We were feared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:25.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Souls who come illegitimately\Nto Soul Society
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:29.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,without the aid of Soul Reapers\Nare called Ryoka,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.44,0:06:33.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and are said to be the cause\Nof all kinds of calamities.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:35.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They think we are enemies?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:39.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:45.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:53.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I am the elder of the Rukon District.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:57.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I witnessed everything that\Nhappened just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:07:02.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We want to welcome you as\NJindanbo's saviors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:10.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There are many rotten Soul Reapers,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.71,0:07:13.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but Jidanbo is a native of\Nthe Rukon District.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:16.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And he's always kind to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:21.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You fought Gin Ichimaru for Jidanbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:24.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you must be\Na good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.16,0:07:29.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…what a terrible wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:34.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:39.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'll heal Jidanbo's wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:44.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Inoue…you can heal that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:47.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:50.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shuno, Ayame!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:01.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hi! Need help?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.57,0:08:03.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:06.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please, lend me your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:11.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly! We are your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:13.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All you have to do is desire it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:14.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Recite the Kotodama – Spirit Chant!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:19.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Soten Kishun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:22.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I reject!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.37,0:08:32.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's amazing, Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:35.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When'd you get that power?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:39.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! Please let me through!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:40.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let me through!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:46.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:50.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's me! Shibata!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:52.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shibata?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:56.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! The parakeet, Shibata!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:57.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:08.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shibata…!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:24.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You put on some weight, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:26.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:30.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you only\Nknew me as a parakeet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:33.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here, you don't change at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:35.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You stay the same as when\Nyou first get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.46,0:09:37.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:40.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shibata…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:42.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Err…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:45.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,About your mother…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:47.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:52.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of run down,\Nbut it's cool during summer and nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.51,0:09:55.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And my family are all really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:57.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Family?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.54,0:10:00.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yuichi, you came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:03.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mom and Dad were worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.59,0:10:06.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:08.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mom and Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.66,0:10:12.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Umm… This boy is Hironari Horiuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:14.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's like my big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:16.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:19.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Like your big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:27.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In Soul Society, or rather\Nthe Rukon District,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:33.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,people who aren't related form\Nfamily-like units and live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:38.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,People who died in different places,\Nat different times, live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:43.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's rare for one to meet up with\Na real family member who died earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:50.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't the Soul Reapers reunite\Nyou with your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:51.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:57.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I died in 1947\Nin Yamanashi Prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.29,0:11:01.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's way before Shibata died.\NOur age, the location, we're far apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:07.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then you haven't seen\Nyour mother yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:10.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, although I'm looking for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:15.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! You have all of us, Yuichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:18.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:23.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're all like him in the beginning,\Nbut we change with time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:27.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I…I won't see my mom again…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:36.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but can I stay with\NShibata for a bit longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.94,0:11:43.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. I'll tell the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:51.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, why are you here, Mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:53.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're not dead, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:55.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No… I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:56.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.83,0:11:59.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder that too…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:03.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? On that rooftop…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:06.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that your Soul Reaper friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:11.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he goes that high up,\Nhe won't be able to see beyond the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:14.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But he'll still keep looking,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:16.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,without giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.83,0:12:19.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of guy Ichigo is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:33.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I was around your age…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.59,0:12:37.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,when I started worrying about my looking\Ndifferent than everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:44.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And I had this amazing strength I couldn’t\Nhandle that was different from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.56,0:12:49.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is this power I got?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:03.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:07.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling that coming here\Nwill give me some clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:09.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I came…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:15.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd risk everything\Nto search for answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:18.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're really giving it\Nyour best, huh Mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:23.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, Yuichi, don’t give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:24.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:27.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep searching\Nwithout giving up,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:28.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you'll find your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:30.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.48,0:13:33.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mister…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:36.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right, let's make a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:38.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:49.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:50.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:56.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What? At least speak up\Nif you’re here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:14:00.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:03.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:18.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Give up breaking through the gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.38,0:14:20.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.76,0:14:23.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Once the gate has been opened,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:26.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the security on the inside\Nbecomes even tighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.96,0:14:30.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which means the same strategy\Nis not the best one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:33.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:35.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What about other gates?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:38.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There won't be much difference\Nwith this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:40.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:45.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If we can't use the gate,\Nwe must enter another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:52.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Elder, do you know\Nthe Kukaku Shiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:54.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:58.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I understand she's someone who\Nconstantly changes residences.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:02.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been able to find out\Nwhere she lives now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:04.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kukaku…Shiba…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:12.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're not planning to go through\Nthe wall with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:14.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.29,0:15:19.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.79,0:15:21.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.16,0:15:26.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.97,0:15:27.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Owwee!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:29.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.55,0:15:35.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A boar?! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:37.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's a boar doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:39.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Owee…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.28,0:15:44.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Darn…thrown again by my Bonnie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.16,0:15:48.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Been a long time, Old Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.37,0:15:52.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ganju, what are you doing here?!\NGo home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.21,0:15:57.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Some greeting! I come to visit after\Na long time and I get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:16:00.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your guests are shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.55,0:16:01.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:06.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:10.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's a dirty Soul Reaper\Ndoing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.71,0:16:12.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:15.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not "what?"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:21.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's a dirty Soul Reaper\Ndoing here, I asked!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:23.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.53,0:16:26.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:30.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Say something, you dandelion head--!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.07,0:16:35.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:37.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You picking a fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:40.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:44.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to goad me like that!\NYou primeval boar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:45.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"Primeval boar"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:47.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we do?!\NWe must stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.58,0:16:48.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:51.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear... Just as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.53,0:16:49.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:51.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I got a name you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.25,0:16:56.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to drink tea!\NWho is that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:17:00.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know who I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:01.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:02.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Neither do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:03.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:04.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even wanna know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:08.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hah… Then it can't be helped.\NI'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:11.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Ganju!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:14.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Self-professed Crimson Bullet\Nof West Rukon District!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:17.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Self-professed the most\N"want-to-call-you-big-brother" candidate
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.75,0:17:20.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,for 14 years running! And…!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.65,0:17:25.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Self-professed West Rukongai's\NTop Soul Reaper Hater!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:28.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All self-professed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:28.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All self-professed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:32.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! You're hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:34.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:36.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:44.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:44.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:48.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! Won't let you get in\NBig Brother's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.84,0:17:51.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you really want to get involved\Nin this fight…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:54.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be your opponents.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:56.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Henchmen…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.71,0:17:57.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.10,0:17:58.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All of them…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:02.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Riding on boars!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:02.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Riding on boars!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:05.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:09.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,While I'm alive, no Soul Reaper\Nwill be allowed to step foot…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.05,0:18:11.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,in West Rukongai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:12.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:14.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:17.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cripes! Cut it out, will ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:20.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna fight, I'll fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.11,0:18:24.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--! You punched\Nmy handsome face…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.31,0:18:27.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,not once, but twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:30.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I kicked you the second\Ntime around, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:35.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, Ichigo! Don't use up your strength\Nin a meaningless fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:38.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He started the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:40.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you want us to stop, tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:45.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh! Getting worked up for\Nsuch a silly thing…the fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:51.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems we're destined\Nto fight, you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:58.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Ganju!\NHe is not an evil Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:19:02.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!\NSoul Reapers are Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.50,0:19:05.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no good or bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:08.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ganju…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:11.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:18.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! Kurosaki doesn't have\Nhis Zanpaku-to!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:19.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:25.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:37.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huge! So that's your Zanpaku-to!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:38.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.37,0:19:45.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you can win\Nwith a bigger sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:55.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:19:59.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.29,0:20:01.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:02.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's like quicksand…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:03.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:10.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--! Using weird tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.59,0:20:25.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, if that didn't drop you,\Nyou're pretty tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.94,0:20:55.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.83,0:21:19.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what time is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.37,0:21:22.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's bad, Big Brother!\NIt's nine already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.79,0:21:26.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?! No!\NCome on, Bonnie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.60,0:21:29.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.46,0:21:31.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bonnie…?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.02,0:21:34.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Continued next week
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:46.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With much appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:48.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,send a rhapsody filled\Nwith treasured thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:52.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the people who have\Nalways held me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:54.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.31,0:21:56.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.31,0:21:58.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever I may be
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:22:00.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll always be grateful for who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.48,0:22:03.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was casually walking through town
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.73,0:22:05.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Around the time dusk fell\Nand the city was bathed in red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.82,0:22:07.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was an afternoon with\Ncrowds of people coming and going
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.02,0:22:09.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know why but\NI just stood there and watched
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.82,0:22:12.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then my cell phone started to vibrate\Nand I made myself move
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:14.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,hoping it could fill\Nin this hole in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.31,0:22:16.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not alone\NYou see, everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.52,0:22:18.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta hold each other up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.57,0:22:20.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With much appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:23.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I send a rhapsody filled\Nwith treasured thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:26.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the people who have\Nalways held me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.31,0:22:28.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.36,0:22:30.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:32.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever I may be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.48,0:22:34.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll always be grateful for who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.61,0:22:38.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The next Bleach:\N"Orihime Inoue's Architectural Visits,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:40.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,will be coming from Kukaku Shiba's\Nhouse in West Rukon District.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.16,0:22:44.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's a gorgeous wooden structure\Nsurrounded by open land.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.38,0:22:47.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's the secret to this building?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.13,0:22:48.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.12,0:22:50.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,These natural wood pillars... Huh?